Comment: 0,0:04:01.63,0:04:04.80,SC_Bottom,夏叶,0,0,0,kara,练好{\fscx50} {\fscx100}Spread the Wings\NSpread the Wings{\fscx50} {\fscx100}を完成させることね
Comment: 0,0:04:05.10,0:04:06.93,SC_Bottom,恋钟,0,0,0,kara,嗯！\Nうん！
